 said: \"O my people! Worship God [alone]: you have no deity other than Him. He brought you into being out of the earth, and made you thrive thereon. Ask Him, therefore, to forgive you your sins, and then turn towards Him in repentance-for, verily, my Sustainer is ever-near, responding [to the call of whoever calls unto Him]!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1534.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":55163,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَإِلَىٰ","translation":"এবং প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55164,"position":2,"arabic":"ثَمُودَ","translation":"সামূদ জাতির","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55165,"position":3,"arabic":"أَخَاهُمْ","translation":"তাদের ভাই","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55166,"position":4,"arabic":"صَـٰلِحًۭا ۚ","translation":"সালিহকে (পাঠিয়েছিলাম)","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55168,"position":5,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55169,"position":6,"arabic":"يَـٰقَوْمِ","translation":"\"হে আমার জাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55170,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱعْبُدُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা ইবাদত করো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55171,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55172,"position":9,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55173,"position":10,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55174,"position":11,"arabic":"مِّنْ","translation":"অন্য কোন","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55175,"position":12,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهٍ","translation":"ইলাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/011_061_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55176,"position":13,"arabic":"غَ