,"audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":62,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ يَٰصَٰلِحُ قَدْ كُنتَ فِينَا مَرْجُوًّۭا قَبْلَ هَٰذَآ ۖ أَتَنْهَىٰنَآ أَن نَّعْبُدَ مَا يَعْبُدُ ءَابَآؤُنَا وَإِنَّنَا لَفِى شَكٍّۢ مِّمَّا تَدْعُونَآ إِلَيْهِ مُرِيبٍۢ","translation":"They answered: \"O Salih! Great hopes did we place in thee ere this! Wouldst thou forbid us to worship what our forefathers were wont to worship? Because [of this], behold, we are in grave doubt, amounting to suspicion, about [the meaning of] thy call to us!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1535.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":55738,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55739,"position":2,"arabic":"يَـٰصَـٰلِحُ","translation":"হে সালিহ","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55740,"position":3,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55741,"position":4,"arabic":"كُنتَ","translation":"তুমি ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55742,"position":5,"arabic":"فِينَا","translation":"আমাদের মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55743,"position":6,"arabic":"مَرْجُوًّۭا","translation":"ভরসা","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55744,"position":7,"arabic":"قَبْلَ","translation":"পূর্বে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55745,"position":8,"arabic":"هَـٰذَآ ۖ","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55747,"position":9,"arabic":"أَتَنْهَىٰنَآ","translation":"আমাদেরকে কি নিষেধ করছো","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55748,"position":10,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55749,"position":11,"arabic":"نَّعْبُدَ","translation":"আমরা উপাসনা করি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_062_012.mp3","c